metadata.name: Da Apefather #001 #1/4
metadata.description:
Dr. Bombay (#001)

Bored Row Records CEO

" db Da Ape AKA Mr. Phire AKA Suge Bright "

Born 3001, here to blaze that ooey gooey funky stuff on the blockchain from infinity to serenity, ya feel me?

I can't burn all these digital trees by myself (well maybe I can) I need y'all help, family.  
Keep it real & never slip on them banana peels. You know the deal we don't eat till everyone got a meal.

Keep the Cadillac runnin' we gone be out the bank in a min...
